blueprint.description:
2.3 GW self sustained power plant with emergency break. Caravan outpost to priority feed of outsourced biocrud.

It needs T.U.R.D. <Selective cutting heads> from "Fastwood forestry upgrade".

Connect to the factory network only with the power pole at the botom left, where the emergency break is.

To start it, connect it to a network with at least 70 MW, add a few hundred wood to the seed maker and add molten salt (around 5k is enough in my testings)

entities.text: This breaks the hold all belt signal, so that only the last fragment maskes the main seed belt to stop for the seeds in the recirculation belt to be able to fit

entities.text:
Emergency break!!!

Cuts the supply to the factory if the power plant is not enough to maintain the supply (accumulator´s charge drops below 50%). 

This way, if there is no other point of connection with the factory network, the power plant will never run out of energy and would run ad infinitum
